		
		
	            Some feature of ATM app:

0.  Choose language
1.  Register and login, check by mail and pass (need to be hidely typed).
	Register: email + pass + bank account number (self user typed)
	+ full name (sur name + first name)
	Login: choose bank
2. Forget password
3.  Show the balance in the account
4.  Withdrawn, print bill
5.  Deposit
	Deposit in the same banking branch, deposit in other banking branch
6.  History
7.  Transfer money to another account, check bank + account number
8.  Bank savings (need virtual time to calculate users' interest)
9.  Setting
	Modify user information
10.  History lookup (by date, by name of receiver or by bank account number
11. Using OTP to sign in
